  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until it is translucent and starting to caramelize.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced Jerusalem artichokes and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the Thai red curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and add the fish sauce, turmeric, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the Jerusalem artichokes are tender.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let the curry simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the curry hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
